author: Home RenoVision DIY
description:
I’m comparing LVP, laminate, hardwood, engineered hardwood, and tile to show you the real differences in durability, waterproofing, installation, and total project cost so you can choose the best flooring for every room in your home. After installing every floor type myself, I’ll test each one and walk you through what to use where, what to avoid, and how to save money on your renovation.If you found this video helpful, please subscribe. Hope you enjoy. Cheers!
